---
title: Hall of Fame
layout: layouts/pokeBase.njk
customcss: "/assets/css/shrines/pokemon/hof.css"
permalink: /shrines/pokemon/hof/
---

<section class="league-hero">
  <p class="league-kicker">Accessed League Records</p>
  <h1>Hall of Fame</h1>
  <p>
    Champion teams, save-file memories, MVPs, and playthrough notes.
    This is where completed adventures get archived like little league records.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="league-section">
  <div class="league-section__heading">
    <p class="league-kicker">Champion archive</p>
    <h2>League records</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="league-grid">
    <article class="league-card league-card--active">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen I / III</span>
      <h3>Kanto</h3>
      <p>FireRed / LeafGreen comfort zone. Current focus: LeafGreen Safari Week prep.</p>
      <small>Status: active save file</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen II / IV</span>
      <h3>Johto</h3>
      <p>Future league memories, rematches, badge quests, and cosy route nostalgia.</p>
      <small>Status: waiting for records</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen III / VI</span>
      <h3>Hoenn</h3>
      <p>Emerald vibes, secret bases, water routes, and Battle Frontier dreams.</p>
      <small>Status: favourite region energy</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen IV / VIII</span>
      <h3>Sinnoh</h3>
      <p>Slow routes, snowy memories, and future team archives.</p>
      <small>Status: record slot open</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen V</span>
      <h3>Unova</h3>
      <p>Dream-team potential, strong story vibes, and room for a proper league log.</p>
      <small>Status: record slot open</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen VI</span>
      <h3>Kalos</h3>
      <p>A stylish little archive slot for future playthrough notes and teams.</p>
      <small>Status: record slot open</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen VII</span>
      <h3>Alola</h3>
      <p>Island challenge records, favourite partners, and champion memories.</p>
      <small>Status: record slot open</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card league-card--galar">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen VIII</span>
      <h3>Galar</h3>
      <p>Shield teams, gym arcs, and powerhouse playthrough notes can live here.</p>
      <small>Status: previous adventure notes</small>
    </article>

    <article class="league-card">
      <span class="league-card__badge">Gen IX</span>
      <h3>Paldea</h3>
      <p>Modern adventure records, favourite catches, and shiny-era memories.</p>
      <small>Status: record slot open</small>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="league-section league-section--template">
  <div class="league-section__heading">
    <p class="league-kicker">Record format</p>
    <h2>What each entry can track</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="record-template">
    <article>
      <span>01</span>
      <h3>Final team</h3>
      <p>Sprites, nicknames, levels, natures, abilities, and final movesets.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>02</span>
      <h3>MVP</h3>
      <p>The Pokémon that carried the run, stole the show, or became weirdly iconic.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>03</span>
      <h3>Save notes</h3>
      <p>Funny moments, painful fights, overlevelling crimes, and favourite memories.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="league-note">
  <p>
    <strong>League note:</strong> this page is ready for proper team records.
    Each region can become a full card once a playthrough is finished.
  </p>
</section>


{% if pokemonPhotos.hof and pokemonPhotos.hof.length %}
<section class="league-section">
  <div class="league-section__heading">
    <p class="league-kicker">Team screenshots</p>
    <h2>Champion memories</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="pokemon-photo-grid pokemon-photo-grid--hof">
    {% for photo in pokemonPhotos.hof %}
      <figure class="pokemon-photo-card">
        <img src="{{ photo.url }}" alt="{{ photo.alt }}" loading="lazy">
        <figcaption>{{ photo.caption }}</figcaption>
      </figure>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}
